365
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:05,140
You write a story through dialogue.

366
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,740
The story called "Charlie, Charlie" was very popular.

367
00:12:08,010 --> 00:12:09,710
The story features a conversation...

368
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:14,250
- between the lead and Charlie.
- It's a conversation between them.

369
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:17,390
