- Exactly.

384
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:49,689
- You see...
- Fan fiction was provocative...

385
00:12:49,690 --> 00:12:52,590
- back then.
- It's like a morning drama.

386
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,289
- It's part of fan culture.
- It's only shared among fans?

387
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:57,129
- Right?
- If anyone asks Charlie a question,

388
00:12:57,130 --> 00:12:58,829
- you answer "Yes" or "No?"
- I answer every question.

389
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:00,500
- I answer every question.
- Charlie, Charlie.

390
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:03,299
Will Yeong Cheol get married in this life?

391
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:04,700
Oh, good question. Charlie, Charlie.

392
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,840
