- Charlie, Charlie.

393
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,370
Yes.

394
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:11,709
- I saw it.
- You saw it?

395
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:12,810
He will get married a bit later.

396
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:15,750
